sexpression.lexer

Interface ITokenVisitor<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - Specify the return type of the visitor execution here.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ATokenVisitor

    public interface ITokenVisitor<E>
    Visitor Design Pattern

    Instances of this interface can visit a Token. Implementers must define a case for every concrete instance of Token.
    See Also:
    Token
